title: GoPro: Introducing GoPro Care
description:
GoPro Care lets you capture your life, no matter how extreme, with no worries. It connects you to GoPro experts who can help you master your camera, offers accidental coverage with camera replacement regardless of location, and more. 

GoPro Care is only available in the U.S.

Shot 100% on the HERO4® camera 

Music 
Hobosexual "Boogie Shuttle"
